I think it would be helpful to have a bit getter helper function:

```c++
inline bool GetBit(std::span<const std::byte> bytes, uint32_t bitpos) noexcept
{
    return (std::to_integer<uint8_t>(bytes[bitpos / 8]) >> (bitpos % 8)) & 1;
